      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·005.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">祈父.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>祈父！予王之爪牙，胡轉予于恤？靡所止居。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Minister of war,
We are the claws and teeth of the king.
Why have you rolled us into this sorrow,
So that we have no abiding place?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
